{"tid":922154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那製造業景氣瀕臨萎縮 PMI跌至2年半新低","createTime":"2018-11-30T06:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T07:14:24.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a69d9e97a330668782dc09765744bb9bd44bc237","tid":922154,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:44:31.000Z","msg":"中國官方今公布，11月製造業PMI（採購經理人指數）由前月50.2降至50，就落在代表景氣榮枯的分界上，創2016年3月以來新低；低於50就表示景氣萎縮。這樣的表現不如預期，經濟學家預估會持平在50.2。<br />\n <br />\n同時，11月非製造業PMI由前月53.9降至53.4，同樣不如市場預期的53.8。綜合PMI更降至去年1月有紀錄以來新低，由10月53.1下滑至52.8。<br />\n<br />\n非官方個PMI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b8828928f2ca228f6975634670b9d5ba070db2","tid":922154,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"跌極都咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da6b6a394959170c8bbc7185f0759efbfc638e1","tid":922154,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40b8828928f2ca228f6975634670b9d5ba070db2","tid":922154,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"跌極都咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"官方，非官方就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f6e883b336587bf30ec6974549533193d4403f","tid":922154,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7d31c1f2183cbaab27fa9514a562efc94255ad","tid":922154,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40b8828928f2ca228f6975634670b9d5ba070db2","tid":922154,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:03:04.000Z